    "notes": "jhgkjh",
    "backstory": "Raised by the tranquil group of monks at the Shrine to Pngo in \u00d6strulade sat upon the Dragon's Nose mountain range. Locran Darter heard tales of of the infinite well in J\u00f6nemn and dreamt of one day gaining powers to provide water to all of those who need it. \nOne day whilst sorting through a box of old and broken trinkets in the church's cellar, he stumbled across a small necklace. Star-shaped chain links held up an obsidian diamond pendant with purple gemstone engravings twisted throughout. As soon as he laid hands on the pendant, visions plagued his mind of tapestries being ripped apart with flashes of Nebulan's constellations.\nAfter panicked research Locran managed to correlate his visions with the continent's capital Qualihah and he has made it his mission to find answers for these intrusive thoughts.",
